  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "HtfyTE9Zr1HB_PIUK0g-U",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 311.41685267857144,
      "y": 129.88950892857133,
      "width": 540.117431640625,
      "height": 2400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2048292364,
      "version": 1778,
      "versionNonce": 1154290484,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778309540398,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Book-my-show\n\nFunctional Requirements\n\n- view the tickets\n- search the tickets\n- Book the tickets\n\nNFR\n- should be scable and should be abailable during peak\nload\n- read >> write\n- consistency >>> availability\n\n--------\nout of scope\n- fault tolerance\n- GDPR\n\n\nCore entities\n- Event\n- venue\n- performer\n- ticket\n- Booking\n\nAPI design\n\nView for shows\nGET /:ShowId -> Res: Event, Performer, venue\n\nSearch for movie\nGET\n/search&text={text}&date={date}&location={location\n} -> Partial<Event>[] \n- [{\nMovie name,\ntheatre name,\ndate & time,\nlocation,\nscreen,\ntotalticket:125, Booked:35, Avaialable: 90,\n}]\n\n\n\nDB design\nMovie \n- id{PK}\n- name\n- actors\n\n\nTheater\n- Id(PK)\n- name\n- location\n\n\nShow \n- Id(PK)\n- theaterId(FK)\n- MovieID(FK)\n- seatId\n\n\nSeats\n- Id(PK)\n- showId(FK) (Index)\n- status: Available, Booked (Index)\n\nSeatCount\n- Id(PK)\n- ShowId(Unique)(FK)\n- AvailableCount\n- BookedCount\n\nA1 - s1\nA2 - s1\n...\nA10 - s1\n\nA1-s2\n...\nA10- s2\n\nTheater-show(1:n)\nMovie-Show(1:n)\nShow - SeatCount(1:1)\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Book-my-show\n\nFunctional Requirements\n\n- view the tickets\n- search the tickets\n- Book the tickets\n\nNFR\n- should be scable and should be abailable during peak load\n- read >> write\n- consistency >>> availability\n\n--------\nout of scope\n- fault tolerance\n- GDPR\n\n\nCore entities\n- Event\n- venue\n- performer\n- ticket\n- Booking\n\nAPI design\n\nView for shows\nGET /:ShowId -> Res: Event, Performer, venue\n\nSearch for movie\nGET /search&text={text}&date={date}&location={location} -> Partial<Event>[] \n- [{\nMovie name,\ntheatre name,\ndate & time,\nlocation,\nscreen,\ntotalticket:125, Booked:35, Avaialable: 90,\n}]\n\n\n\nDB design\nMovie \n- id{PK}\n- name\n- actors\n\n\nTheater\n- Id(PK)\n- name\n- location\n\n\nShow \n- Id(PK)\n- theaterId(FK)\n- MovieID(FK)\n- seatId\n\n\nSeats\n- Id(PK)\n- showId(FK) (Index)\n- status: Available, Booked (Index)\n\nSeatCount\n- Id(PK)\n- ShowId(Unique)(FK)\n- AvailableCount\n- BookedCount\n\nA1 - s1\nA2 - s1\n...\nA10 - s1\n\nA1-s2\n...\nA10- s2\n\nTheater-show(1:n)\nMovie-Show(1:n)\nShow - SeatCount(1:1)\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WqdJSipvY1hBnf07t9zlm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 945.377232142856,
      "y": 1240.3571428571408,
      "width": 448.33978271484375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
